# {Title} - Screen Prototype

Astro prototype generated by the `shaping-screens` skill.

## Run locally

```bash
pnpm install
pnpm dev
```

Open `http://localhost:4321/` to navigate the sitemap, each screen, and each state.

## File layout

- `src/pages/index.astro` - sitemap
- `src/pages/{screen}.astro` - one file per screen
- `src/components/StateSwitcher.astro` - state-switching component
- `src/styles/global.css` - design tokens
- `src/transitions.json` - screen-transition state machine
- `spec.md` - summary for downstream skills (input when promoting the prototype to real implementation)

## Inspecting states

Each screen accepts `?state=loading|empty|error|success` as a URL query.
The StateSwitcher rendered at the top of the screen also links to each state.

